  "tasbihatArba3Title": "TASBIḤĀT AL-ARBAʿA",
  "tasbihatArba3Subtitle": "Bisomwa muri raka'a ya 3 n’iya 4",
  "tasbihatArba3Info": "Mu mategeko ya Shia, Tasbiḥāt al-Arbaʿa isimbura Surah al-Fatiha muri raka'a ya 3 n’iya 4 ya Dhuhr, Asr, Maghrib na Isha. Kuyisoma inshuro imwe ni itegeko (wājib), kandi kuyisoma inshuro eshatu birashishikarizwa (mustaḥabb).",
