  "tasbihatZahraOriginLabel": "Inkomoko",
  "tasbihatZahraHadith": "Lady Fatima al-Zahra (sa) yasabye Intumwa ﷺ umukozi. Irababwira iti: \"Ese singakwereka ikintu cyiza kurusha ibyo? Soma Subḥānallāh inshuro 33, Alḥamdulillāh inshuro 33, na Allāhu Akbar inshuro 34 nyuma ya buri sengesho. Ibyo bikurusha umukozi.\"",
