  "tasbihatDuaAyatKursiSource": "Surah al-Baqarah 2:255",
  "tasbihatDuaAyatKursiNote": "Uwasoma Āyat al-Kursī nyuma ya buri sengesho ritegetswe, nta kindi gishobora kumubuza kujya mu ijuru uretse urupfu. Imam al-Bāqir (a) yavuze ko ari imwe mu mirongo ikomeye cyane muri Qur’an.",
